{
  "title": "Mutations",
  "publicationStatus": "public",
  "subtitle": "",
  "about": [
    "Quickly jump back and forth between the DNA and the protein it codes for by using the **Show DNA** and **Show protein** buttons.",
    "",
    "Try editing the entire DNA strand and entering in your own sequence by using the **Edit DNA** button, or click **Show DNA** and then mutate the strand by clicking on one of the nucleotides.",
    "",
    "What effect (if any) does your mutation have one the protein that gets produced? Are some types of mutations more serious than others?"
  ],
  "fontScale": 0.75,
  "models": [
    {
      "id": "page3$0",
      "url": "imports/legacy-mw-content/converted/sam-activities/DNA-to-proteins/page3/page3$0.json",
      "viewOptions": {
        "controlButtons": "",
        "enableKeyboardHandlers": false
      },
      "modelOptions": {
        "DNA": "ATGCCAGGCGGCGAGAGCTTGCTAATTGGCTTATAG",
        "DNAState": "dna"
      }
    }
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "transcribe",
      "text": "Transcribe",
      "action": [
        "if (DNAStateAfter('transcription-end'))",
        "  set('DNAState', 'dna');",
        "animateToDNAState('transcription-end');"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "translate",
      "text": "Translate",
      "action": [
        "if (DNAStateBefore('translation:0') || get('DNAState') === 'translation-end')",
        "  set('DNAState', 'translation:0');",
        "animateToDNAState('translation-end');"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "reset",
      "text": "Reset",
      "action": "reset();"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "stop",
      "text": "Stop",
      "action": [
        "if (DNAStateBefore('translation-end')) stopDNAAnimation();",
        "else stop();"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "next-state",
      "text": "Continue one step",
      "action": "animateToNextDNAState();"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "dna-dialog",
      "text": "Edit DNA",
      "action": "openDNADialog();"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "show-protein",
      "text": "Show protein",
      "action": "set('DNAState', 'translation-end');"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "show-dna",
      "text": "Show DNA",
      "action": "set('DNAState', 'dna');"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "start",
      "text": "Start/continue model",
      "action": [
        "if (DNAStateBefore('translation-end')) animateToDNAState('translation-end');",
        "else start();"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "label",
      "text": "Click on a nucleotide to perform a mutation or "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "buffer",
      "text": "|"
    }
  ],
  "layout": {
    "model-bottom": [
      ["label", "dna-dialog"],
      ["show-dna", "transcribe", "buffer", "translate", "show-protein"],
      ["next-state", "start", "stop", "reset"]
    ]
  },
  "template": [
    {
      "id": "model-bottom",
      "left": "model.left",
      "top": "model.bottom",
      "width": "model.width",
      "align": "center"
    }
  ]
}